<BaseLayout title="About — AIBolt Labs" description="About AIBolt Labs, an independent open-source software lab.">
  <section class="page-hero"><div class="shell"><div class="eyebrow">About the lab</div><h1 class="page-title">Independent by design.<br />Open by practice.</h1><p class="lead">AIBolt Labs is a place for software ideas that need careful engineering before they need a large audience.</p></div></section>
  <section class="section"><div class="shell intro-grid"><div><div class="rule-heading">Purpose</div><h2 class="section-title">Make unusual ideas dependable enough to leave the lab.</h2></div><div><p class="lead">We are interested in the space between a visual prototype and a reusable system: lifecycle, semantics, accessibility, performance, integration, and the small operational details that determine whether a good idea survives contact with a real application.</p><p class="section-copy">The work is developed with modern engineering tools, including LLM-assisted workflows, and reviewed against the same public code, tests, browser behaviour, and release evidence expected of any maintained project.</p></div></div></section>
  <section class="section section-divider"><div class="shell"><div class="rule-heading">Working principles</div><div class="method-grid"><article class="method-item"><span class="number">01</span><h3>Cause before spectacle.</h3><p>An effect should make its origin and ownership understandable. Movement without a reason belongs outside the product.</p></article><article class="method-item"><span class="number">02</span><h3>Contracts before convenience.</h3><p>We document lifecycle, cleanup, accessibility, and performance boundaries—not only the shortest installation snippet.</p></article><article class="method-item"><span class="number">03</span><h3>Evidence before claims.</h3><p>Packages, tests, working demonstrations, and source history carry more weight than polished concept language.</p></article></div></div></section>
  <section class="section-tight"><div class="shell open-callout"><div><div class="eyebrow">Follow the work</div><h2>The repository is the primary record.</h2><p>See current source, releases, issues, and contribution guidance directly on GitHub.</p></div><a class="button" href="https://github.com/aibolt">Visit GitHub ↗</a></div></section>
</BaseLayout>
